works.description: We have seen some luxurious earphones in the past, and the latest we have with us comes from the house of Japan-based Final Audio Design. The firm has added four new models to its high-end Piano Forte Series. Inspired by horn loudspeakers, the Piano Forte Series earphones promise to enrich audiophiles with sound quality, as they will experience inside a concert hall. One of the salient features of the Piano Forte is the driver unit, which comes integrated with a light diaphragm installed inside the metallic housing.
